				<wikidot:authorName>Thekillerax</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1832151</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is amazing. The only thing that bothered me was this sentence:</p> <blockquote> <p>Robodude watched as the Supreme Stabbinator flailed around on its back as managing to make small circles on the floor, but it was unable to lift itself off the wet concrete.</p> </blockquote> <p>I'm not entirely sure if that sentence is grammatically sound, and even if it is, it sounds awkward. I believe it'd be better as:</p> <blockquote> <p>Robodude watched the Supreme Stabbinator flail helplessly on its back as it managed to make small circles on the ground, but was ultimately unable to lift itself off the wet concrete.</p> </blockquote> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
